{"tid":2478342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[學習歷史] 國父借革命而沽名釣譽 以起義名義大肆斂財中飽私囊","createTime":"2021-04-07T03:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T04:38:46.000Z","uid":108201,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"98a6273acdc81e20b01e2bbbf73daca9b71dac04","tid":2478342,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:52:04.000Z","msg":"借古喻今，請對號入座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n李燮和在1909年這個「罪狀十二條、善後辦法九條」，後來公開刊發時名為《南洋革命黨人宣佈孫文罪狀傳單》，是「第二次倒孫風潮」時陶成章等人為攻擊孫中山所炮製的重磅炸彈。<br />\n<br />\n在這篇《孫文罪狀》中，孫文被重筆描繪成「傾南山之竹，書罪無窮；決東海之波，流惡無盡」之人。其「罪狀」分為「殘賊同志」五項、「蒙蔽同志」三項、「敗壞全體名譽」四項，三大類十二項。<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">指責孫文借革命而沽名釣譽，以起義名義大肆斂財中飽私囊</span></strong></span>，「香港、上海匯利銀行，貯款二十萬。」而孫文<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">不支持《民報》、大力扶持《中興日報》是為了控制輿論；成立南洋支部「架空總會」</span></strong></span>，目的是「欲使其權歸一人，以便其營私之念而已。」更誣陷孫文排除異己，對於不合己意、觸怒他的人，不惜用<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>告密、陷害甚至下毒等惡毒手段，</strong></span></span>「國人皆曰可殺」。"},{"pid":"df22d69569766e52cdabc6a1071c223f9b3412eb","tid":2478342,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:55:49.000Z","msg":"無人睇歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0cb8be07f639333a2b42a321186c6fbe0a6001","tid":2478342,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:56:53.000Z","msg":"不嬲都知孫中山係個asshole<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656fa02fe7514ef85b25cfd0ff113f07699894ec","tid":2478342,"uid":261522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T03:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食幼齒最叻！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\"